    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="duk.00419.001_large.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">Burlington VT.</name>
                    <date when="1890-12-08">Dec 8, 1890.</date>
                </dateline>
                <salute>Bro Walt,</salute>
            </opener>

            <p>I wrote last time that Han<ptr target="n0285"/> was better</p>

            <p>The prevailing severe cold weather at present retards her convalescence a
                little&#8212;Dreadful cold, and the character, or effect of the atmosphere <choice>
                    <sic>allmost</sic>
                    <corr>almost</corr>
                </choice> neutralizes all the warmth that might be obtained from the hottest coal
                fire&#8212;It makes me very apprehensive&#8212;</p>

            <p>I hope you are as well, or</p>

            <pb xml:id="leaf001v" facs="duk.00419.002_large.jpg" type="verso"/>

            <p>comfortable as when last you wrote&#8212;Small book recd</p>

            <closer>
                <salute>Gratefully Yours,</salute>
                <signed>Charlie</signed>
            </closer>

            <postscript>
                <p>Time stagnant, in every thing</p>
            </postscript>

        </body>
